data.description: Wonderful Home nestled in on a large, fenced, shaded lot. This 3- or 4-bedroom home offers a cozy Livingroom with Wood burning fireplace. Kitchen is open to the dining area the downstairs flows nicely through out! 2 BR and 1 bath down or use one as an office. 2BR and 1 bath upstairs. Tons of built-ins in the living room, kitchen, dining, upstairs bedroom, laundry room and the entry. Truly custom home. Fabulous deck out back off the living room perfect for entertaining, cooking, and relaxing. Neighborhood is quite lovely, very established and welcoming. You really have to come see this jewel to appreciate everything is has to offer. Call for your appointment. 24hr notice preferred.
